(27, 'Beta Greens New Cairo', NULL, '<p>Beta Egypt for Urban Development is one of the fastest growing Real Estate developers in the Egyptian market since 1993. Headquartered in Heliopolis, Cairo &ndash; Beta Egypt has investments worth 6 billion Egyptian pounds with landmarks created through fully holistic and blissful communities. Beta Egypt focuses on creating high-end housing communities that cater to meet Egypt&rsquo;s emergent market demand. Beta Egypt celebrates 25 years of successful operations that have led to the creation of gated communities with over 3000 families living within its sustained communities in 6th of October and Obour City. Beta Egypt focuses on building happy communities that redefine living standards, by putting your desires and aspirations first.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>previous projects:</p>\r\n<p>-Beta Greens 6</p>\r\n<p>-Golf residence</p>\r\n<p>-Golf palace</p>\r\n<p>-Beta gardens</p>\r\n<p>-Golf house</p>\r\n<p>-Golf corner</p>\r\n<p>-Beta club house</p>\r\n<p>-Beta greens</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Beta Greens New Cairo&rdquo; offers an integrated component mix creating an exceptionally happy community with privacy,serenity and an unrivaled lifestyle within a spectacular green environment. With its strategic location,stretching across 25 acres of private and pristine landscape with a fantastic assortment of luxury apartments, matchless town and twin houses and luxurious leisure and entertainment. It&rsquo;s true anti dote to the demands of modern life to rejuvenate, relax and enjoy the tranquility of contemporary living. &ldquo;Beta Greens&rdquo;invites you to celebrate a happy life all year round. With its strategic location, the development is a retreat stretching across 85 acres of private and pristine landscape that allows its residents to enjoy the extensive green expanses surrounding the 730 homes in this mixed-use complex.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p