(33, 'Green Avenue', NULL, '<h3>Brief About New Capital</h3>\r\n<p>The location of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/New_Administrative_Capital_of_Egypt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">the new administrative capital</a>&nbsp;is located on the borders of the city of Badr in the area</p>\r\n<p>between Suez Road and Ain Sokhna road east of the regional ring road,</p>\r\n<p>after New Cairo and the cities of the cities and the future city and the city of Sunrise and Fifth Avenue and away from Ain Sokhna about 60 km and also 60 km The heart of the Greater Cairo Governorate.</p>\r\n<p>The administrative capital area is about 170 thousand acres.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Brief About New Jersey</h3>\r\n<p>A well-known company was chosen to undertake the construction of this edifice after</p>\r\n<p>its overwhelming success in many construction and real estate marketing businesses,</p>\r\n<p>a pioneering company in the field of building and construction.</p>\r\n<p>New Jersey Real Estate Development Company is the most famous in the entire Arab world</p>\r\n<p>and indeed all over the world.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Previous projects:</p>\r\n<p>1-L&rsquo;amour mini compound (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>2- future mall 1 (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>3- future mall 2 (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>4- future plaza (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>5- 90 residential building (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>6- 70 residential villas (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>7- medical center (al shrouk)</p>\r\n<p>8- new Heliopolis compound (new Heliopolis)</p>\r\n<p>9- future mall (badr city)</p>\r\n<p>10- L&rsquo;amour mini compound (new cairo)</p>\r\n<p>11-L&rsquo;amour al- andalus mini compound (new cairo)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>New Jersey Development Company</h3>\r\n<p>New Jersey Development Company includes the best and most famous engineers in engineering design.</p>\r\n<p>The village of Green Avenue, the new administrative capital, has been built by a large elite of engineers, technicians,</p>\r\n<p>and workers with the most accurate and flexible work.</p>\r\n<p>The latest construction equipment and tools in the world.</p>\r\n<p>The building materials used on the Green Avenue site are the new, high-quality administrative capital.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Location &amp; Area Of Green Avenue</h3>\r\n<p>Our new project exists in R7 in the new capital near the diplomatic district, near BUE, the exhibition ground, the embassy district and also near the Green River</p>\r\n<p>Green Avenue is held on 11.5 acre</p>\r\n<p>The area divided Between residential, commercial &amp; green area</p>\r\n<p>20% of the project ( Buildings )</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Facilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Swimming Pool</li>\r\n<li>Kids Area</li>\r\n<li>Commercial Area</li>\r\n<li>Healthy Club</li>\r\n<li>Restaurants &amp; Cafes</li>\r\n<li>Track</li>\r\n<li>Security 24\\7</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&bull;جرين أفينيو-العاصمة الإدارية الجديدة</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;&nbsp;-خبرة فى المجال العقارى لاكثر من 18سنة</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">- أرض مميزة ، نسبة البناء 18.5%،على السيتى واك ، فرع من افرع النهر الاخضر</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;- بمنطقة R7&nbsp;امام اكبر جامعة انترناشيونال بالعاصمة الادارية مما يضمن لك اقصى معدلات الاستثمار.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">-</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">يمكن اضافة حمامات سباحة خاصة في بعض الواحدات بناءً على طلب العميل</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;- مساحة المشروع 11.6 فدان مساحة كافية لضمان الخصوصية. كما يقع المشروع علي ٢ شوارع رئيسية و ممشى City Walk.</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"ql-align-right\">- يحتوي المشروع عن نادي صحي خاص لسكان جرين أفنيو