(55, 'PYRAMIDS MALL', NULL, '<p><strong>BRIEF ABOUT THE NEW ADMINISTRATIVE CAPITAL</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>The location of the new administrative capital is located on the borders of the city of Badr in the area</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Between Suez Road and Ain Sokhna road east of the regional ring road,&nbsp;</strong><strong>after New Cairo and the cities of the cities and the future city and the city of Sunrise and Fifth Avenue and away from Ain Sokhna about 60 km and also 60 km The heart of the Greater Cairo Governorate.&nbsp;</strong><strong>The administrative capital area is about 170 thousand acres</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>BRIEF ABOUT THE DEVELOPER</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>PYRAMIDS DEVELOPMENTS is one of the leading companies which working in REAL</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>ESTATE field in France since 1999 and started to develop its projects in Egypt in 2013.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Caring of all Pyramids company employees in transforming the new ideas and the vision of the board of directors which is built for changing the Egyptian real estate market and raising it to a level that is competitive globally in terms of the possibilities and services provided to all pyramids company projects investors. The selection of all the employees is based on their equipped and the ability to developing and serving all Pyramids company customers in line with the vision of the board of directors.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Pyramids Chooses its First Compound in a prime location in the new administrative capital of Egypt area R7 plot no.N2 with Fully Finished residential units such as (Apartments, Duplex, Penthouses and Studios) with Facilities that help Egyptians to find all their life needs.</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Project details</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Location: Part No. COM17</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Number of floors: ground and 5 floors</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Spaces: commercial from 12m</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Load Percentage: 30%</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Maintenance: 10%</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Payment systems</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>5% down payment and 5% after 3 months - installments up to 8 years</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>10% down payment - and installments up to 10 years</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>25% immediate downpayment - post-receipt installment</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>30% down payment - 12% immediate return for 2.5 years and installment after handover</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>35% down payment - 14% immediate return for 2.5 years and the premium after handover</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>40% down payment - 16% immediate return for 2.5 years and installment after handover</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>The prices</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Commercial - from 90 to 230 thousand per meter</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Services</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Customer service for the project</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Fire fighting system</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>A specialized management company</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Movable seats for people with special needs</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Children\'s area</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Solar energy systems</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Electronic portals</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, 'PYRAMIDS', 29, 'en', '2021-01-17 17:19:55', '2021-01-17 17:22:42'),
(56, 'PYRAMIDS MALL', NULL, '<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>نبذة عن العاصمة الجديدة</u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>موقع العاصمة الادارية الجديدة يقع على حدود مدينة بدر بالمنطقة بين طريق السويس وطريق العين السخنة شرق الطريق الدائري الإقليمي ، بعد القاهرة الجديدة ومدن مدن ومدينة المستقبل ومدينة الشروق والتجمع الخامس ويبعد عن العين السخنة بحوالي 60 كم وأيضاً 60 كم قلب محافظة القاهرة الكبرى. مساحة العاصمة الإدارية حوالي 170 ألف فدان</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>نبذة عن المطور</u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>شركة PYRAMIDS DEVELOPMENTS هي واحدة من الشركات الرائدة التي تعمل في مجال العقارات في فرنسا منذ عام 1999 وبدأت في تطوير مشاريعها في مصر في عام 2013.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>رعاية جميع العاملين بشركة بيراميدز في تحويل الأفكار الجديدة ورؤية مجلس الإدارة التي تهدف إلى تغيير سوق العقارات المصري والارتقاء به إلى مستوى تنافسي عالميًا من حيث الإمكانيات والخدمات المقدمة لجميع الأهرامات مستثمرو مشاريع الشركة. يعتمد اختيار جميع الموظفين على تجهيزهم وقدرتهم على تطوير وخدمة جميع عملاء شركة بيراميدز بما يتماشى مع رؤية مجلس الإدارة.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>تختار بيراميدز كمبوندها الأول في موقع متميز بالعاصمة الإدارية الجديدة بمصر المنطقة R7 قطعة أرض رقم N2 بوحدات سكنية كاملة التشطيب مثل (شقق ، دوبلكس ، بنتهاوس ، استوديوهات) مع التسهيلات التي تساعد المصريين على إيجاد جميع احتياجات حياتهم.</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>تفاصيل المشروع</u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>الموقع : القطعه رقم COM17</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>عدد الأدوار: أرضي و 5 دور</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>المساحات: التجارى من 12م</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>نسبه التحميـل: من %30</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>الصيانه : 10%</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u></u>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>نظم السداد</u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>5% مقدم و 5% بعد 3 شهور &ndash; تقسيط حتي 8 سنوات</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>10% مقدم &ndash; و تقسيط حتي 10 سنوات</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>25% مقدم فوري &ndash; القسط بعد الإستلام</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>30% مقدم &ndash; بعائد فوري 12% لمدة 2.5 سنة و القسط بعد الإستلام</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>35% مقدم &ndash; بعائد فوري 14% لمدة 2.5 سنة و القسط بعد الإستلام</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>40% مقدم &ndash; بعائد فوري 16% لمدة 2.5 سنة و القسط بعد الإستلام</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>الاسعار</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>تجاري &ndash; من 90 الي 230 الف للمتر</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong><u>خدمات</u></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>خدمة عملاء خاصة بالمشروع</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>نظام مكافحة الحرائق</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>شركة إدارة متخصصة</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>مقاعد متحركة لذوي الاحتياجات الخاصة</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>منطقة للأطفال</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>أنظمة الطاقة الشمسية</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><strong>بوابات الكترونية</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, 'PYRAMIDS', 29, 'ar', '2021-01-17 17:19:55', '2021-01-17 17:23:40'),
(57, 'ZA MALL', NULL, '<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Za Mall New Capital</strong></span><br />The Mall of the New Administrative Capital is in the most beautiful and famous areas of the New Capital in the Down Town area, which is the largest commercial areas within the Administrative Capital and the most vital areas in the New Administrative Capital, and this is because it is close to many landmarks, malls and other compounds, and this makes The Mall project is a very suitable opportunity for investment.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>The company developing the Za Mall New Capital project</strong></span><br />The Mall project is developed by <strong>Zaytoun Developments</strong>, one of the leading companies in the field of real estate development that has great experience in the field of real estate development, and the company chose a very special location in the new administrative capital, and Zaytoun Real Estate Development Company was keen to provide all the important services inside the mall.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>The Mall New Capital Location:</strong></span><br />The Za Mall New Capital is located in the heart of the New Administrative Capital in the Downtown commercial area, which is characterized as the largest commercial areas that are located between many vital areas within the Administrative Capital.<br />The Za Mall New Capital is also located near many important areas within the Administrative Capital, it is located in front of the main entrance to the New Administrative Capital, and this distinctive location makes it near the most famous landmarks of the New Capital and this makes it a very special location.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14pt;\"><strong>Services provided in the New Capital Mall</strong></span><br />The Za Mall New Capital enjoys many wonderful and distingui