(75, 'POINT 9 MALL', NULL, '<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><u>Information about Point 9 Administrative Capital</u></strong></span><br /> Point 9 Mall New Capital is the first project of Capital Hills Development, and it is the latest commercial projects within the New Administrative Capital, especially in the Downtown area, as it is distinguished by its location near many vital areas within&nbsp;the Administrative Capital.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><u>Information about the developer</u></strong></span><br /> Capital Hills Real Estate Company, which is one of the largest real estate companies in Egypt, and it is a pioneer in the development and construction of lands inside Egypt, and Capital Hills Real Estate participates in the construction of Point 9 Mall, the administrative capital, with a large real estate consultant, Arch Plan D.&nbsp;Ayman, and you will be one of the largest consulting firms in Egypt.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><u>Location:</u></strong></span><br /> Located in a very privileged location in the Administrative Capital in the Downtown commercial area in plot mu1 / 14, which is considered the largest commercial areas within the New Administrative Capital, which is located between many vital areas, and Point 9 Mall New Capital is located near Important areas, most notably:</p>\r\n<p>Al Massa Hotel.<br /> Banks area.<br /> Government district.<br /> Central station.<br /> Point 9 Mall services<br /> Backup power system.<br /> CCTV cameras.<br /> Sound system.<br /> Central shower.<br /> Firefighting system.<br /> Central air-conditioning.<br /> Solar system.<br /> Land scape.<br /> Panoramic elevator.<br /> Double glazed exterior.<br /> Modern and luxurious interior design.<br /> Parking.<br /> 2 entrance.<br /> Super Lux finishing offices.<br /> Theater for shows and parties.<br /> Food Court District.<br /> A sophisticated spa mirror.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decorat